Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=34}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Marinheiros venceram?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venceram, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:48.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's getting clearer now. - CR}Ah, está ficando mais claro agora.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Whitebeards have lost? - CR}{The Whitebeard Pirates lost? - Yibis}Os Piratas do Whitebeard perderam?{arch/Munlyte}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did the Marines really win? - CR}Os Marinheiros realmente venceram?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:56.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Regarding the war occurring at Marineford being waged by the Whitebeards and we, the Marine HQ, - CR}{Regarding the war at Marineford between/Nthe Whitebeard Pirates and Marine Headquarters, - Yibis}{\q2}A guerra em Marineford entre\Nos Piratas do Whitebeard e o Quartel-General da Marinha{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:59.43,Main-207+,,0,303,0,,{\i1}{Regarding the war occurring at Marineford being waged by the Whitebeards and we, the Marine HQ, - CR}{Regarding the war at Marineford between/Nthe Whitebeard Pirates and Marine Headquarters, - Yibis}{\q2}A guerra em Marineford entre\Nos Piratas do Whitebeard e o Quartel-General da Marinha{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:04.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the process took longer than anticipated\Nbecause of the enemy's persistence - CR}{the process took longer than anticipated\Ndue to the enemy's tenacity. - Yibis}levou mais tempo do que o previsto\Ndevido à tenacidade do inimigo.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:08.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but the Marines all\Nfought with a sense of justice - CR}{However, the Marines who fought for justice - Yibis}Porém, ao final de uma luta árdua\Nem nome da justiça,{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:13.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and defeated all the\NWhitebeards and their allies - CR}{have prevailed over the Whitebeard Pirates\Nand their allies. - Yibis}nossos Marinheiros prevaleceram sobre\Nos Piratas do Whitebeard e seus cúmplices.{arch+Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:19.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and now we are happy to tell you that\Nthe Marines HQ gained a complete victory... - CR}{We are happy to report that the\NMarine Headquarters has achieved total victory! - Yibis}Temos a alegria de informar que o Quartel-General\Nda Marinha alcançou a vitória total!{Ravenfire}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conseguiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:30.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Marines are invincible!\NPraise all our heroes! - CR}Os Marinheiros são invencíveis!\NViva os nossos heróis!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:40.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want to be called to\Nduty at the HQ someday! - CR}{I want to transfer to Headquarters someday! - Yibis}{One day, I'll be one of those\NMarines summoned to Headquarters! - arch}Mal posso esperar pelo dia em que eu for\Ntransferido pro Quartel-General!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A guerra acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes! - CR}Viva!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad! - CR}Ainda bem!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The legendary pirate - Whitebeard lost! - CR}{The legendary pirate Whitebeard was defeated! - Yibis}O lendário pirata Whitebeard\Nfoi derrotado!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A guerra acabou, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes! You're safe now! - CR}Sim, estamos seguros agora!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is so great! - CR}Isso é ótimo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conseguiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos seguros!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:09.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurrah for the Marines! Hurray\Nfor the World Government! - CR}Viva os Marinheiros!\NViva o Governo Mundial!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:14.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And for victory and justice\Nand peace! Hurrah! - CR}{And for victory, justice, and peace! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! - Yibis}E pela vitória, justiça e paz:\NHip! Hip! Hurra!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:17.67,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! - CR}– Hip! Hip! Hurra!\N– Hip! Hip! Hurra!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:31.08,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{At the scene of the war - Marineford!\NThere are 7 ships out at sea! - CR}Sete navios espreitam nas águas\Npróximas ao campo de batalha que foi Marineford.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.25,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those who would take part in the new era... - CR}{Those who would shoulder\Nthe coming pirate era - Yibis}{With the coming pirate era\Nlying on their shoulders, - arch}{With the coming pirate era\Nplaced on their shoulders, - arch}Peças-chave da nova era pirata...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:38.63,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{...are there to witness this\Ngreat turning point in history. - CR}{have come to witness\Nthis historic turning point. - Yibis}{they needed to witness\Nthis historic turning point. - arch}se reuniram para testemunhar\Neste ponto de virada histórico.{arch/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.29,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Staring at the dust of the battle\Nrising above Marineford - - CR}{Surveying the dust settling over Marineford— - Yibis}Observando a poeira da batalha\Nse erguendo sobre Marineford—{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:45.87,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,evidência do funcionamento\Nda justiça na Grande Era Pirata—{CR}{proof of the order that reigns\Nin the Great Pirate Era— - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:50.24,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{they sense the restlessness\Nof the changing of the times. - CR}{they grasp the seething unrest of the times. - Yibis}eles sentem a inquietação dos tempos de mudança.{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Captain Drake. - CR}Capitão Drake...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:55.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente... acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Marines have to change, also. - CR}{The Marines will have to change too. - Yibis}Isso vai forçar os Marinheiros a mudarem também.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In no time... - CR}{It won't be long before - Yibis}{It won't be long now - arch/Munlyte}Em breve...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:07.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whitebeard's territory will sink in\Na sea of blood in this whirlpool. - CR}{Whitebeard's territory devolves\Ninto a chaotic sea of blood. - Yibis}{before Whitebeard's territory devolves\Ninto a chaotic sea of blood. - arch/Munlyte}O território do Whitebeard vai afundar,\Nsugado num turbilhão de sangue.{Z/Barry}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard é a chave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:15.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He has gained new followers\Nand Whitebeard's power. - CR}{He has new followers\Nand Whitebeard's power. - Yibis}Ele ganhou novos seguidores\N{\i1}e{\i0} o poder do Whitebeard.{arch/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:19.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure they're gonna reign for while! - CR}Tenho certeza de que eles serão\No olho do furacão por um bom tempo!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:27.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's all... his fault! - CR}Tudo... É tudo culpa dele!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:30.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou caçar ele logo, logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go! To the New World! - CR}Vamos pro Novo Mundo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do que você tá falando, Apoo{-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:44.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That guy will become his enemy.\NIs he really gonna save him? - CR}{Those guys are bound to become rivals.\NIs he really gonna save him? - Yibis}Esses caras vão acabar se tornando inimigos.\NEle vai mesmo salvar ele?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô falando do Trafalgar Law.\NEle é conhecido pela crueldade.{CR}{I'm talking about Trafalgar Law.\NHe's known for his cruelty. - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:56.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He wouldn't save Straw Hat Luffy\Nif there wasn't some catch. - CR}Ele não salvaria o Chapéu de Palha Luffy\Nsem algum motivo oculto.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's odd. - CR}{Strange. - Yibis}Que estranho.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Captain Hawkins? - CR}O que foi,\NCapitão Hawkins?{Z/arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:09.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been trying to see the\Nodds that Luffy's still alive - CR}{I've repeatedly checked the odds of Straw Hat Luffy's survival, - Yibis}Não importa quantas vezes eu consulte\Nas chances de sobrevivência do Chapéu de Palha Luffy,{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but it never reaches zero. - CR}{but they're never zero. - Yibis}elas não chegam a zero.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra ser sincero, eu fiquei com medo\Nquando a guerra começou,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas agora o grande pirata Whitebeard está morto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então realmente acabou, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:34.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's over?! - CR}Como assim, "acabou"?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:42.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The new force who emerged during this\Nwar--that Blackbeard is quite a guy! - CR}{That Blackbeard is quite a guy!\NHe came out of this war a major power. - Yibis}Esse Blackbeard é mesmo impressionante!\NEssa guerra consolidou ele como uma grande potência.{arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:48.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The New World is ruled by the Four Emperors. - CR}O Novo Mundo é controlado\Npelos Quatro Imperadores:{arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:53.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whitebeard, "Red-Haired", Kaido, Big Mam. - CR}Whitebeard, Ruiva, Kaido e Big Mom.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But since one of them is dead, - CR}Mas com um deles morto,{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the world is out of balance,\Nand no one can predict the consequences! - CR}o mundo perdeu o equilíbrio\Ne ninguém sabe o que vai acontecer!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:05.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Este é o começo de uma nova era\Ncomo ninguém jamais viu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.44,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The news of the Marine victory\Nin the war at Marineford, - CR}A notícia da vitória da Marinha\Nna batalha de Marineford,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.72,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{the biggest war since the beginning\Nof the Great Pirate Era, - CR}{the biggest conflict since the\Nbeginning of the Great Pirate Era, - Yibis}o maior conflito desde\No início da Grande Era Pirata,{Ravenfire}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.77,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{spread all over the world\Nin the blink of an eye - CR}se espalhou pelo mundo num piscar de olhos,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.63,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and people are celebrating\Nthe news everywhere. - CR}e as pessoas em todo lugar comemoraram.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.25,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{East Blue. - CR}O East Blue...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.63,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,{Hurrah! - CR}Viva!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:36.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos seguros agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou tão feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.02,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{West Blue. - CR}O West Blue...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The sea will be in peace now! - CR}{The sea will be at peace now! - Yibis}O mar finalmente vai estar em paz!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurrah! - CR}Viva!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.09,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{South Blue. - CR}O South Blue...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.25,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,{We're gonna have a bargain sale today! - CR}Grande promoção hoje!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So are we! - CR}A gente também!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Marinheiros venceram!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:55.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que alívio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.36,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{North Blue. - CR}O North Blue...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim! Estou tão feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos beber, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have tons of it! - CR}Tem pra todo mundo!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.78,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Grand Line. - CR}A Grand Line...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.73,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,O que a gente vai fazer amanhã?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.08,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,Eu quero brincar de pega-pega!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.58,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,Esconde-esconde!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright! - CR}{– Whoo!\N– Yay! - Yibis}– Boa!\N– Eba!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:18.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{God! Thank you! - CR}{Oh God, thank you so much!  - Yibis}Meu Deus, somos muito gratos!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:25.43,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like most of history, some facts are\Ntrimmed off as the news goes around - CR}{Like most of history, some facts\Nare omitted as the news spreads, - Yibis}{\q2}Como é comum ao se fazer história,\Nalguns fatos ficam pra trás conforme a informação viaja,{arch/Raven/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:30.14,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and just the two words\N"Marine victory" stand out. - CR}{and just the two words,\N"Marine victory," are what stand out. - Yibis}e as palavras "vitória da Marinha"\Ncorrem à frente de todo o resto.{arch/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:35.02,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The people, in their excitement at the\Nnews, failed to notice something... - CR}{The world, in its excitement over the news,\Nfailed to notice something. - Yibis}{With the world in excitement over the news,\Nits people fail to notice something... - arch}As pessoas, em sua empolgação com\Na notícia, não perceberam algo...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:37.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{W-What's going on?! - CR}Que isso...?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look at you people! That's hilarious! - CR}{Look at you fools! It's hilarious! - arch}Olha pra vocês, seus idiotas! Que piada!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:49.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard disse que o grande\Ntesouro One Piece é real!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou encontrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:09:00.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is so much more out there! Let's set sail! - CR}Tem muito mais por aí! Vamos zarpar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:13.13,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Marine victory. The result is not necessarily peace... - CR}{A victory for the Marines\Ndoes not necessarily mean peace. - Yibis}{A victory for the Marines\Nneed not mean certain peace. - arch}{A victory for the Marines\Nwill not always bring peace. - arch/Z/Raven}Uma vitória da Marinha... O resultado\Npor si só não garante a paz.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:21.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Y-You can't come any further!\NDon't come into our town! - CR}{D-Don't come any further!\NStay away from our town! - Yibis}N-Não chegue mais perto!\NFique fora da nossa cidade!{arch/Raven/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:27.56,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{With the loss of a deterrent -\Nnamely, the threat of Whitebeard - - CR}{With the loss of Whitebeard as a deterrent, - Yibis}Com Whitebeard não estando mais presente\Npara servir como dissuasão,{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:32.33,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{the world of the seas has\Nbecome very unsettled... - CR}os mares se tornaram muito mais perigosos.{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:40.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. I turned all\Nthe Marines to stone. - CR}Não se preocupe. Eu transformei todos os Marinheiros em pedra.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E aí, como o Luffy está?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É grave? Ele vai se recuperar, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How did you know that we\Nwere gonna surface here? - CR}Como você sabia onde a gente ia emergir?{arch/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:54.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was scared thinking that the\NMarines were still chasing us. - CR}Eu tava apavorada achando que os\NMarinheiros ainda estavam nos perseguindo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I made Salome follow you underwater. - CR}Eu mandei a Salome seguir vocês por baixo d'água.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:02.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não mude de assunto, seu bicho peludo!{CR}{Don't change the subject, you furry beast! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– So weak!\N– So weak! - CR}– Que fraco!\N– Que fraco!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, Captain! - CR}Ah, Capitão!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.72,Main-207+,,0,0,15,,Eu fiz tudo o que pude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer que... ele está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:19.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos estabilizá-lo. Porém...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:22.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...he took greater damage than you think. - CR}{he took more damage than you'd believe. - Yibis}ele sofreu danos inimagináveis.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is no guarantee\Nthat he will survive yet. - CR}Eu ainda não posso garantir que ele vai sobreviver.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's no wonder! - CR}O que você esperava?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who's talking? - CR}Quem disse isso?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Straw boy couldn't even\Nstand up at Impel Down once! - CR}{Back at Impel Down,\NStraw-boy could not even stand up! - Yibis}Lá em Impel Down,\No garoto de palha mal conseguia ficar em pé!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Straw Hat was risking his life! - CR}O Chapéu de Palha arriscou a vida!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We got out of the prison thanks to him! - CR}{It's because of him that we even escaped! - Yibis}Só conseguimos escapar por causa dele!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:47.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because of him, we can \Nmake our dream come true: To go to the Kamabakka Kingdom! - CR}Graças ao Chapéu de Palha, nosso sonho de ir pro\NReino de Kamabakka vai se tornar realidade!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go! - CR}{Let us now set a course! - arch/Munlyte}Vamos traçar o rumo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:52.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{this is it for my role in supporting Straw-boy. - CR}Da Newkama Land\Npro coração do Newkamadom!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They are prisoners of Impel Down. - CR}Quem diabos são eles?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like they're Luffy's friends. - CR}São prisioneiros de Impel Down.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They have snuck into the ship. - CR}Parece que o Luffy fez amizade com eles.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe that he\Npushed himself that hard! - CR}Eles se esconderam no navio.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! - Yibis}Sim!{Ravenfire}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:09.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe that he\Npushed himself that hard! - CR}A determinação dele é espantosa!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:13.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's how much he wanted\Nto save his brother Ace! - CR}Foi tudo isso que ele quis\Npra salvar o irmão dele, o Ace!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:17.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! We know how much\Nhe pushed himself to do it! - CR}É verdade! Todos nós vimos\No quanto ele se esforçou!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:22.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But that brother died in front of his eyes... - CR}Mas o irmão dele morreu... bem na frente dele...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...in order to protect him... - CR}tudo pra protegê-lo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:32.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is no justice in this world! It's\Nnot surprising that he broke down! - CR}Não existe justiça nesse mundo!\NNão é surpresa que ele tenha desmoronado!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:36.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Aguenta firme, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You got to live! You got to, Straw Hat! - CR}Você tem que viver! Tem que viver, Chapéu de Palha!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que tragédia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:51.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wish I could take his place! - CR}Quem dera eu pudesse tomar o lugar dele!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Poor Luffy! - CR}Meu pobre Luffy!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que inveja...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must be nice to have the Pirate\NEmpress care about you that much... - CR}{Must be nice for the Pirate Empress\Nto care about you that much. - Yibis}Deve ser bom ter a Imperatriz Pirata\Nse preocupando tanto assim com você.{arch/Raven}
Comment: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah... - CR}Uh-huh.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, are you a friend of Straw boy? - CR}A propósito, você\Né amigo do garoto de palha?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:08.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, I didn't have to save him at all. - CR}Não... e eu não tinha nenhuma obrigação de salvá-lo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're wondering about my motivation,\NI can come up with a reason. - CR}{I could make up a reason\Nif simple kindness concerns you. - Yibis}Se você quer saber o que me motivou,\Neu posso inventar uma razão.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, that's okay. Sometimes your\Ninstinct tells you what to do. - CR}{No, that is okay. Sometimes\Ninstinct just drives you. - Yibis}Não, tudo bem.\NÀs vezes as pessoas agem por instinto.{Polly/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{--Hey, wait!\N--You can't walk around yet! - CR}Ei, espera! Você não pode sair andando ainda!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:23.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{--Don't push yourself like that!\N--He told you to rest! - CR}Não se esforce assim!\NEle mandou você descansar!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The wound could open up! - CR}O ferimento pode reabrir!{Ravenfire/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Where are you going? - CR}P-Pra onde você tá indo?!{Ravenfire}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é o Trafalgar Law\Ndo North Blue, não é?
Comment: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:46.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, is it okay for you\Nto move around like that? - CR}Querida, pode mesmo se\Nmovimentar nesse estado?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você salvou a minha vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You must rest. It could kill you. - CR}{You need bed rest. This could kill you. - Yibis}{Go and sleep. You could die. - arch/Munlyte}Você precisa de repouso. Pode morrer.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't ease my mind. It's impossible! - CR}Minha mente não consegue descansar. Não tem como!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:02.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What I have just lost\Nwas too important to me! - CR}O que eu acabei de perder era importante demais pra mim!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:07.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That is why I know that Luffy-kun\Nmust be going through far worse! - CR}É por isso que eu sei que o Luffy\Nestá passando por algo muito pior!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:13.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At least, his instinct to protect himself forced him to lose consciousness at that time! - CR}{At least his survival instincts forced him\Nto lose consciousness back there! - Yibis}Foi uma misericórdia o instinto de sobrevivência\Nter forçado ele a perder a consciência!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if he survives, - CR}Mesmo que ele se recupere,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:20.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't stop worrying about\Nthe moment that he wakes up. - CR}eu não consigo parar de me preocupar\Ncom o momento em que ele acordar.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You, fuzzy beast, - CR}{You! Furry beast! - Yibis}Você! Bicho peludo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{do you have a Transponder Snail? - CR}Você tem um Caramujo Telegráfico?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É... quer dizer... Sim, senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:39.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que inveja... Ele parece um servo dela.
Comment: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah... - CR}Mm-hmm.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:45.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna call the Kuja's ship so we can go\Nacross the Calm Belt even with this submarine. - CR}Eu posso pedir pro navio das Piratas Kuja levar\Neste submarino pela Calm Belt.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:50.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If the Government finds out that Luffy's\Nalive, they're gonna come after him! - CR}Se o governo descobrir que o\NLuffy está vivo, eles {\i1}vão{\i0} atrás dele!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let us harbor him at the Maiden Island! - CR}Eu vou dar abrigo a vocês na Ilha das Mulheres.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:53.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - CR}O quê?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:14:00.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If they still see me as a\NWarlord, Luffy can rest safely! - CR}Enquanto eu for uma das Guerreiras do Mar,\No Luffy pode descansar em segurança!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:23.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Almirante de Frota Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here you are! - CR}Estava te procurando!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've had word from Impel Down! - CR}Recebemos notícias de Impel Down!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is Magellan alright? - CR}O Magellan está bem?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He got beaten badly and is barely alive. - CR}{He was badly beaten and is on death's door. - Yibis}Ele foi espancado quase até a morte.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:38.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's been treated intensively\Nby the medical team. - CR}{As we speak, the medical team\Nhas him under intensive care. - Yibis}Neste momento, a equipe médica\No tem em cuidados intensivos.{Ravenfire}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:43.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's a dutiful man - he's blaming himself. - CR}Ele é um homem dedicado; parece que\Nestá assumindo toda a responsabilidade.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:47.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They said that if he could\Nmove now, he'd kill himself. - CR}{They're saying, were he able to move about,\Nit would possibly end his life. - Yibis}{Were he able to move about,\Nhe might very well take his own life. - arch}Estão dizendo que se ele pudesse\Nse mover, acabaria com a própria vida.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:50.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let him do such stupid thing! - CR}Não deixem ele fazer essa besteira!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What has been going on at the prison? - CR}Qual é a situação da prisão?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Allow me to tell you the\Ncondition as it stands. - CR}{I'll get you up to speed. - Yibis}{I'll report on that now. - arch}Deixe-me informá-lo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:03.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The situation on Level 6 is especially bad.\NIt's literally a disaster. - CR}A situação no Nível 6 é especialmente ruim.\NÉ um desastre total lá embaixo.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um desastre?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:15.18,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What's up? - CR}E aí, pessoal?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:19.60,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You prisoners're doomed to\Nbe stuck behind bars forever! - CR}{You prisoners are doomed\Nto wallow away behind bars forever! - Yibis}{[/q2]You prisoners, doomed to wallow away behind bars forever! - arch}Prisioneiros como vocês estão condenados\Na definhar atrás das grades pra sempre!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:24.47,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got nothing to do except wait to die! Then how about this?! - CR}Vocês todos estão esperando a morte chegar,\Nentão que tal isso?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:28.34,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you fight each other in the cell?! - CR}Por que vocês não lutam\Naté a morte nas celas?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:35.48,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I will free those of you who\Nsurvive as members of my crew! - CR}Eu vou libertar os sobreviventes...\Ne colocá-los na minha tripulação!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.71,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.22,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Me tira daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.32,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let me be your crew member! - CR}{I'll win a place on your crew! - Yibis}Eu vou ganhar um lugar na sua tripulação!{arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:55.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So he has freed selected members from\Nthe worst criminals in the world?! - CR}{So that's how he freed\Nthe world's most notorious inmates?! - Yibis}Então ele escolheu os prisioneiros mais\Ninfames do mundo e os libertou?!{arch/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes. But only 4 prisoners were taken. - CR}Sim... mas apenas quatro prisioneiros foram levados.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:03.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{San Juan Wolf, Avalo Pizarro,\NVasco Shot, Catarina Devon. - CR}Sanjuan Wolf, Avalo Pizarro,\NVasco Shot e Catarina Devon.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:09.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But there are obviously more\Nprisoners missing from level 6! - CR}Mas claramente há outros\Nprisioneiros desaparecidos do Nível 6!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que significa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:25.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I understand. Then, there are\Nmore escapees from level 6! - CR}Entendo. Isso significa que\Nhá mais fugitivos do Nível 6!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:30.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se até mesmo um dos fugitivos do Nível 6\Nchegar a algum país,{CR}{If even one of the fugitives from Level 6\Nreaches a country somewhere, - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the people will be in grave danger! - CR}{the citizens will be in grave danger! - Yibis}os cidadãos estarão em grave perigo!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Check to see how many there were. - CR}Descubram quantos eram.{arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get their names, and put a\Nmost wanted list out now! - CR}{Get their names and put together\Na most wanted list now! - Yibis}Consigam os nomes deles e montem\Numa lista de procurados imediatamente!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:47.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, I... - CR}Bem, eu... é que...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:51.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm under orders from the World Government - CR}{The World Government has\Nruled that this incident... - Yibis}O Governo Mundial ordenou\Nque este incidente no Nível 6...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{to keep this level 6 matter secret. - CR}{is to be covered up! - Yibis}seja abafado!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:53.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{ - CR}O quê?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:58.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{More blunders will harm the\NGovernment's reputation. - CR}{Any more blunders on our part will cause\Na loss of confidence in the government. - Yibis}{Any more blunders on our part will affect\Nthe world's confidence in the government. - arch}Mais erros da nossa parte vão\Nprejudicar a reputação do governo.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Malditos!{CR}{That's absurd! - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:34.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You bastard! - CR}Seu desgraçado...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:43.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Moria, you're too weak to go\Non with the title as a Warlord. - CR}Moria, você ficou fraco, o que significa\Nque não serve mais como Guerreiro do Mar.{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:51.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"Died in the War of the\NBest" sounds better than "done in by the Government." - CR}{"Died in the Summit War" has a much better\Nring to it than "Done in by the Government." - Yibis}"Morreu na Guerra do Melhor" soa muito melhor\Ndo que "Eliminado pelo Governo."{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:56.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whose idea was this?! Sengoku?! - CR}De quem foi a ideia?! Do Sengoku?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:18:00.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, someone much higher up the ladder! - CR}{No... Much higher than that. - Yibis}Não... Ainda mais acima.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:28.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A pirate ship is approaching\NLascamp, West Blue! But bases in that area have no ships! - CR}{Pirates are nearing Lascamp in the West Blue!\NBut bases in the area have no ships for a counteroffensive! - Yibis}{Pirates are nearing Lascamp in the West Blue! But bases in the area have\Nno more ships for a counteroffensive! - arch}{\q2}Piratas se aproximando de Lascamp no West Blue,\Nmas as bases de lá não têm navios pra contra-atacar!{Yibis/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The nearest bases outside of that area are... - CR}{Codes for the next nearest bases?! - Yibis}Códigos das bases mais próximas?!{Ravenfire}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:32.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The 80th division will send back-up! - CR}{The 80th Branch will send backup! - Yibis}A 80ª Divisão vai enviar reforços!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is South Blue checking \Nthe location of the site! - CR}South Blue informando. Local confirmado!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:46.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought pirates would be afraid of us after killing\NWhitebeard and gaining victory! - CR}{\q2}Eu achei que os piratas iam ter medo da gente depois que\Nmatamos o Whitebeard e vencemos a batalha de Marineford!{Yibis\Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:50.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Instead of laying low, they\Nare going wild everywhere! - CR}Em vez de se esconderem,\Neles estão causando caos por todo lado!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que deu neles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Pirates have made a raid on Lascamp! - CR}Piratas desembarcaram em Lascamp!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We lost touch with the site! Send back-up! - CR}{We have lost touch with them!\NSend backup! - Yibis}Perdemos as comunicações. Enviem reforços!{arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repito, enviem reforços para Lascamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:07.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Carreguem os suprimentos!\NVamos rumo à Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.23,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Two weeks after the War of the Best, - CR}Duas semanas após a Guerra do Melhor,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:19.34,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{people start to seeing\Neffects around the world. - CR}{people around the world\Nstart seeing its impact. - Yibis}as pessoas ao redor do mundo\Ncomeçam a sentir os impactos.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:27.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Y-You can't come any further!\NDon't come into our town! - CR}N-Não chegue mais perto!\NFique fora da nossa cidade!{arch/Raven/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês ouviram as notícias, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vocês sabem que esta ilha\Nnão é mais território do Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This symbol is meaningless now! - CR}Esse símbolo não significa mais nada!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! Whitebeard is dead! - CR}É isso aí! Whitebeard está morto!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:11.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen, and engrave this in your mind! - CR}Escutem bem e gravem isso na memória!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The man who takes control of\Nthis island from today is me - - CR}A partir de hoje, esta ilha pertence a mim,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:17.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the pirate Brownbeard! - CR}o grande pirata Brownbeard!{Munlyte}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:25.34,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The war ended with the death of\NWhitebeard and the victory of the Marines. - CR}A guerra terminou com a morte do Whitebeard\Ne a vitória da Marinha.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:28.07,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{But contrary to what the Marines thought, - CR}Mas ao contrário do que a Marinha esperava,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:33.44,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3860,5360,1,\c&H000000&)}{the situation has grown\Ntense all over the world. - CR}os mares ao redor do mundo mostram\Nsinais de cair em desordem.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.45,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Meanwhile, a short time ago, - CR}Um pouco antes,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:42.55,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hancock, Jimbei and others decided to head to the Maiden Island to harbor the unconscious Luffy - CR}{[/q2]Hancock, Jinbe, and the others decided to harbor\Nthe unconscious Luffy on the Isle of Women. - Yibis}{\q2}Hancock, Jinbe e os outros decidiram abrigar\No inconsciente Luffy na Ilha das Mulheres.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.99,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and joined up with the Kuja's ship. - CR}{They have rendezvoused with the Kujas' ship. - Yibis}E agora se encontraram\Ncom o navio das Kujas.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alright then, - CR}Bom, então...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:53.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{this is it for my role in supporting Straw-boy. - CR}meu papel em apoiar o garoto de palha acabou.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Irrá!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you mind if I leave the\Nrest up to you, Jimbei? - CR}{Should I leave the rest up to you, Jinbe? - Yibis}Posso deixar o resto com você, Jinbe?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes. I can't swim as I want yet. - CR}Sim. Eu ainda não consigo nadar mesmo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The least I can do is stay\Nhere until he gets well. - CR}O mínimo que posso fazer é ficar aqui\Naté o Luffy{-kun} se recuperar.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não sei como posso ajudá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was a curious turn of fate to meet you. - CR}Que reviravolta curiosa do destino ter te encontrado.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:15.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Concordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:21.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although we were both locked up in\Nthe greatest prison in the world - Impel Down, - CR}Estávamos ambos presos na maior\Nprisão do mundo, Impel Down,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)}{if it weren't for Luffy-kun, - CR}mas se não fosse pelo Luffy,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:28.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}{we would have never met each\Nother at all I suppose. - CR}{I suppose we would have never met at all. - Yibis}acho que nunca teríamos\Nnos encontrado.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:35.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}{We both tried really hard to keep up\Nwith Straw boy at Marineford, didn't we? - CR}{You and I tried really hard to keep up\Nviith Straw-boy at Marineford, right? - Yibis}Nós dois nos esforçamos muito pra acompanhar\No garoto de palha em Marineford, não é?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's hard to say goodbye to you - CR}É difícil dizer adeus a você,{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:43.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I have sweet candies waiting\Nfor me to come back to the kingdom. - CR}mas eu tenho uns docinhos\Nesperando meu retorno ao reino.{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:46.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, cuide bem do garoto de palha!
Comment: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:47.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Aye. - Yibis}Mm-hmm.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:54.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tchau, Chapéu de Palha! Obrigado por nos libertar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:58.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu sonho pode se realizar graças a você!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Diz oi pra ele quando ele acordar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:04.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See you again if we have a chance! - CR}Até a próxima, se tivermos a chance!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:05.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aguenta firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não pode morrer, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's go! - CR}Certo, vamos nessa!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:15.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To the New Kamas' home and our mecca! - CR}Pro coração do Newkamadom\Ne o lugar que sonhamos em ver!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:16.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Reino de Kamabakka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Irrá...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:23.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3345,4330,\c&H000000&)}{We have to head for the Maiden Island, too. - CR}{We have to head for the Isle of Women too. - Yibis}{We must head off too, for the Isle of Women.- arch}Precisamos começar a ir\Npra Ilha das Mulheres.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:26.66,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Duas semanas se passaram.{CR}{Two weeks later, - Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:33.60,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Law and others are staying in the bay to provide Luffy with treatment. - CR}{Law and the others are staying\Njust off the coast to treat Luffy. - Yibis}Law e sua tripulação estão ancorados\Nperto da costa para tratar o Luffy.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:47.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é perigoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:49.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se acalma, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:52.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is going to happen\Nif we leave him like that? - CR}O que vai acontecer se a gente deixar ele assim?{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:56.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, it's simple. - CR}{Well, it's like I said - Yibis}Bom... é simples.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:01.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like I said when we got here, if his wound opens up, he will die. - CR}{when we got to this island, if his wound opens up, he'll die. - Yibis}Como eu disse quando chegamos nesta ilha,\Nse o ferimento abrir, ele morre.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, now is the chance! - CR}{Yes, now is our chance! - Yibis}Sim! Agora é a nossa chance!{arch/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me solta, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fica quieto, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I said "let me go"! - CR}Eu disse me solta!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:17.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê o Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:22.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:22.08,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Ele tá fora de controle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:23.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's Luffy! - CR}{Luffy will... - Yibis}Luffy...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We got to tell Snake Princess-sama! - CR}Precisamos avisar a Princesa Serpente!{Z}
Comment: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:25.72,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:30.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Snake Princess-sama! Snake Princess-sama! - CR}Princesa Serpente! Princesa Serpente!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:32.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy woke up! - CR}O Luffy acordou!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:33.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{--Luffy-sama?! - CR}– Mestre Luffy...?!\N– Mestre Luffy...?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really?! - CR}É verdade?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:38.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad. I wanna see him right away! - CR}Que bom. Eu quero vê-lo imediatamente!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can't, Snake Princess! - CR}{\i1}Não{\i0}, você não pode, Princesa Serpente!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.20,0:23:43.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everybody wants to see him. - CR}Todo mundo quer ver o Luffy.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:47.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can't discipline your people if\Nyou allow yourself to go and see him. - CR}Suas ordens não terão {\i1}nenhum{\i0} peso\Nse você se permitir ir vê-lo.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Men are prohibited on this island. - CR}Homens {\i1}não{\i0} podem pisar nesta ilha!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:55.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We let strange men stay at the bay area - CR}Estamos permitindo homens estranhos\Nficarem perto da costa;{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:58.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and that's enough of an exception for us! - CR}{\i1}não podemos{\i0} fazer mais exceções!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:00.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Before that, Big Sis,\Nyou need to eat something. - CR}{Before that, you need to eat something. - Z}Você precisa comer alguma coisa primeiro, irmã mais velha.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:08.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right, Big Sis!\NYou've barely eaten since you got back! - CR}É verdade, irmã querida! Você mal\Ncomeu desde que voltou!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:11.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! Luffy must be very hungry, too! - CR}{That's right!\NLuffy must be very hungry, too! - Yibis}É verdade! O Luffy também deve estar morrendo de fome!{Z/arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:15.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fix a lot of great dishes\Nthat will give him energy! - CR}Preparem uma montanha dos nossos\Nmelhores pratos pra restaurar a energia dele!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:16.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, com prazer!\N– Sim, com prazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna help you! - CR}{I will help you! - Yibis}Eu vou ajudar!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.67,0:24:21.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ladies, let's do it now! - CR}{Ladies, let's get to it! - Yibis}Vamos lá, senhoras!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.17,0:24:23.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Snake Princess-sama! - CR}– Sim, Princesa Serpente!\N– Sim, Princesa Serpente!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:28.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I should just let her do that. She\Njust wants to fix some food... - CR}Não devo pressioná-la mais.\NEla só quer preparar comida.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:29.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then... - CR}E quando terminarem...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.81,0:24:33.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna take them to him! - CR}Eu vou pessoalmente levar tudo até ele!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.38,0:24:33.05,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you're going?! - CR}Então você {\i1}vai{\i0} mesmo?!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:38.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We promised that when he gets\Nwell, we would invite Luffy alone. - CR}Combinamos que quando ele melhorar,\Nvamos receber apenas o Luffy.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:40.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere por esse momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.42,0:24:44.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't! I am an empress!\NDon't tell me what to do! - CR}Eu não consigo! Eu sou uma imperatriz!\NVocê não manda em mim!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.23,0:24:48.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I said [/i1]nyo[/i0]! The whims of our current ruler do\N[/i1]nyot[/i0] take precedence over national traditions! - Yibis}{I said [/i1]nyo[/i0]! The whims of our current ruler\Ndo [/i1]nyot[/i0] supersede [/i1]nyational[/i0] traditions! - arch/Raven}Eu disse {\i1}não{\i0}! {\i1}Nada{\i0} deve\Nse sobrepor às nossas tradições nacionais!{Z/arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.43,0:24:53.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Honestly! You're infected\Nby such a strong virus! - CR}Sinceramente! Ela foi infectada\Npor um vírus tão forte!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.97,0:24:58.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe that the fearful\Npirate empress has become lovesick! - CR}Eu {\i1}não{\i0} acredito que a temida\NImperatriz Pirata ficou apaixonada!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.04,0:25:03.08,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, he must have been like a small ant - CR}No entanto... ele deve ter\Nsido como uma formiguinha...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:06.65,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{diving into a tempest at\NImpel Down and the Marine HQ. - CR}mergulhando numa tempestade em Impel Down\Ne no Quartel-General da Marinha.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:11.62,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must have been an act of God to let\Nhim live and be brought back here. - CR}Só pode ser intervenção divina que\Npermitiu que ele sobrevivesse e chegasse até aqui.{Yibis/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.62,0:25:16.76,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder what God expects from him. - CR}{I wonder what they expect from him. - Yibis}O que será que os céus esperam dele.{arch/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.03,0:25:19.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, me passa a chave de fenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.86,0:25:21.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.57,0:25:24.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Você acha que consegue consertar o navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:26.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, eu me viro.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:28.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mudando de assunto, pra onde o Chapéu de Palha foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Jimbei is gone, too. - CR}O Jinbe também sumiu.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:33.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know. - CR}Não sei te dizer.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.01,0:25:39.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, I heard that if a man enters the Maiden Island, he's gonna be turned to stone - CR}{Well, I heard that if a man enters the\NIsle of Women, he'll get turned to stone. - Yibis}Bom, eu ouvi dizer que se um homem entrar\Nna Ilha das Mulheres, ele é transformado em pedra.{Ravenfire/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.62,0:25:41.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but maybe it's worth dying for. - CR}Mas talvez valha a pena morrer por isso.{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.69,0:25:47.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{According to Aphelandra-chan, not\Nall women were there at the port. - CR}{According to Aphelandra-chan, only some\Nof the women were there at the port. - Yibis}Segundo a Aphelandra, só um punhado\Ndas mulheres estava no porto.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.12,0:25:52.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The female-only island that I dreamed\Nof! I wish I could take a look inside! - CR}{The island full of women that I dreamed of!\NI wish I could take a look inside! - Yibis}Uma ilha cheia de mulheres. É como um sonho!\NQueria tanto poder dar uma espiada lá dentro!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.06,0:25:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're gonna die, you idiot. - CR}Você ia morrer, seu idiota.{arch/Raven}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.20,0:25:56.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que tem ursos fêmeas...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.27,0:25:57.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's Maiden Island! - CR}– É a Ilha das {\i1}Mulheres{\i0}!\N– É a Ilha das {\i1}Mulheres{\i0}!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.07,0:25:59.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.34,0:26:01.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só humanos! Só tem humanos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.81,0:26:04.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:43.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde estou?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.55,0:26:48.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Maybe it was all a dream... - CR}Talvez... tenha sido tudo um sonho.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.84,0:27:06.48,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2951,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Me desculpa... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.47,0:27:13.78,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2588,3310,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{I couldn't make it all the way. - CR}{I couldn't be saved. - Yibis}{You tried to save me, but I still went and died. - arch}Não havia como me salvar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.95,0:27:27.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai embora! Vai embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.36,0:27:28.63,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(857,1270,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.96,0:27:32.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No! - CR}Para!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.10,0:27:43.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai embora! Vai embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.65,0:28:25.18,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I don't escape death... - CR}{If I can't avoid death, - Yibis}Se eu não sair dessa vivo...{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.58,0:28:29.95,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(4221,4740,0.5,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{I'm sorry, but could you/Nlook after my brother? - CR}poderia cuidar do meu irmão?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.42,0:28:35.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A guerra acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.29,0:28:36.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ace-san is... - CR}O Ace já não–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.73,0:28:39.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não diz isso! Não fala nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.07,0:28:43.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu já me belisquei...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.13,0:28:45.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{hard enough to rip my skin! - CR}forte o bastante pra rasgar a pele!{arch/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.34,0:28:50.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If it were a dream, I should've woken by now! - CR}{If it's a dream,\NI'd be awake by now! - Yibis}Se fosse um sonho, eu já teria acordado!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.18,0:28:55.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é um sonho, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.42,0:29:08.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Ace está morto mesmo, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.27,0:29:18.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, ele está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.01,0:29:29.35,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey grandpa, who is Ace? - CR}{Hey Grandpa, who's Ace? - Yibis}Ei, vovô, quem é esse tal de "Ace"?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.35,0:29:32.55,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2223,3210,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{Oh, he is... - CR}Ah, ele é...{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.82,0:29:36.92,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{...the guy who will become your brother! - CR}o cara que vai ser seu irmão mais velho!{Yibis}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:42.83,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! I'll see you at the\Ntop of the pirates' world! - CR}Luffy! Te vejo no\Ntopo do mundo pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.83,0:29:46.23,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(1990,3410,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{Come to the top! - CR}Vem, me encontra no topo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.98,0:30:05.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=17}Ace!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=35}===============================DIALOGUE============================
